skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: illini laundry
des: This skill connects to the laundry alert API to retrieve current laundry data from all UIUC dorms. Simply ask Alexa for laundry information at a specific dorm and she will respond with the number of washers and dryers available at the specified location.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
